19
00:01:32,832 --> 00:01:36,663
笙ｪI pass through the crowd with you笙ｪ

20
00:01:40,544 --> 00:01:44,512
笙ｪAs if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other笙ｪ

21
00:01:46,033 --> 00:01:48,399
Welcome, Mr. Lan.

22
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,466
