23
00:01:50,466 --> 00:01:51,680
Alright, no problem.

24
00:01:54,176 --> 00:02:00,260
笙ｪPiecing them together flawlessly,
you give it back to me笙ｪ

25
00:02:01,427 --> 00:02:05,280
笙ｪStars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart笙ｪ

26
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:09,152
笙ｪI make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star笙ｪ

27
00:02:09,152 --> 00:02:11,136
笙ｪOpen my secret笙ｪ

28
00:02:11,136 --> 00:02:16,773
笙ｪI hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you笙ｪ

29
00:02:16,773 --> 00:02:20,645
笙ｪSinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper笙ｪ

30
00:02:20,645 --> 00:02:25,344
笙ｪWith each breath,
I can feel the sweetness笙ｪ

31
00:02:25,344 --> 00:02:31,033
笙ｪTwo lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate笙ｪ

32
