34
00:02:39,066 --> 00:02:42,499
Yifu Dashienski once said
the best design is the taste.

35
00:02:43,733 --> 00:02:45,533
Insightful.

36
00:02:50,304 --> 00:02:56,203
笙ｪWhen the loneliness cracks,
