44
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:38,200
Sit, Miss Jin.

45
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:38,933
Alright.

46
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:45,633
I am Lan Chen's grandfather, Lan Rensha.

47
00:03:45,666 --> 00:03:51,133
Welcome to the banquet jointly held
by the Gu family and us.

48
00:03:51,266 --> 00:03:55,266
Tonight, all drinks are non-alcoholic.
Please feel free to enjoy.

49
00:03:55,666 --> 00:03:59,633
As everyone knows, we and the Gu family
have been friends for generations.

50
00:04:00,666 --> 00:04:04,466
Mr. Gu and I worked hard
when we were young.

51
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:10,366
We supported each other
and established our foundations.

52
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,966
Decades have passed
in the blink of an eye.

53
00:04:13,433 --> 00:04:15,552
Now it's the era of the young people.

54
00:04:16,633 --> 00:04:20,866
My grandson, Lan Chen,
and Mr. Gu's granddaughter, Gu Qianqian

55
00:04:20,933 --> 00:04:23,133
