for both our families.

58
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,933
Won't we meet Zeng Huaishi
from Lihuai International?

59
00:04:54,368 --> 00:04:59,966
Qianqian, you're sitting so far away.
Come sit next to Chen.

60
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:04,466
You two were childhood friends.

61
00:05:04,833 --> 00:05:10,033
They weren't happy if we didn't let them
sit together back then. Come here.

62
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:24,366
I thought it would be a banquet
with Lihuai International,

63
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:28,366
